"\t"

#. type: Content of: <refentry><refsect1><refsect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"<placeholder type=\"indexterm\" id=\"0\"/> Carries the necessary "
"configuration parameters for a DRBD device of the enclosing resource. This "
"section is very similar to the <option>on</option> section.  The difference "
"to the <option>on</option> section is that the matching of the host sections "
"to machines is done by the IP-address instead of the node name. Required "
"parameters in this section: <option>device</option>, <option>disk</option>, "
"<option>meta-disk</option>, all of which <emphasis>may</emphasis> be "
"inherited from the resource section, in which case you may shorten this "
"section down to just the address identifier. <placeholder type="
"\"programlisting\" id=\"1\"/>"
msgstr ""
